com.cheetah.recorder

Class BucketResults

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.cheetah.recorder.BucketResults

  • public class BucketResults
extends java.lang.Object
    A simple structure returned whenever the LatencyBucket is emptied. Contains the average of all entries, as well as the number of entries at the time of emptying.
    Since:
    1.0.0
    Version:
    1.0.0, 2019-12-05
    Author:
    Alex Gaudreault
